snippet.title: Game Dev Unlocked
snippet.description: Hi, my name is David and I make indie games full-time; games like The First Tree! I like focusing on content for newcomers and experienced devs alike, so stop on by, put your legs up, and let's learn how to make (and finish!) some games.
